+ \"\\\"\");\r\n    }\r\n    return new PSQLException(GT.tr(\"Cannot cast to boolean: \\\"{0}\\\"\", String.valueOf(value)),\r\n        PSQLState.CANNOT_COERCE);\r\n  }\r\n\r\n}\r\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777643141538}}
